<英文法規名稱>Regulations Governing Establishment of Foreign Curriculum Departments and Classes in Private Senior High Schools and Below</英文法規名稱>
<中文法規名稱>私立高級中等以下學校外國課程部班設立辦法</中文法規名稱>
